{"type":"message","id":"99de60f1","parentId":"36d9b5f6","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:00:59.737Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:19","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <title>MingoX - Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"MingoX - 多语言多媒体内容平台，用文字、图片、播客等形式分享新闻、思想与见解。Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"./\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"./\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"./about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <div class=\"site-intro\">\n                    <h1>🎙️ MingoX</h1>\n                    <p class=\"site-tagline\">Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages</p>\n                    <p class=\"site-desc\">用文字、图片、播客等多种形式，分享新闻、思想与见解</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <h2 class=\"page-title\">📰 最新发布</h2>\n\n                <ul class=\"post-list\">\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-elderly-ai-learning-needs.html\">👵 老年人AI学习需求研究<br><small class=\"title-en\">Study on Elderly AI Learning Needs: 6 Types & Standards</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ AI, 老年研究</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-elderly-ai-learning-needs.html\">基于237位老年人深度访谈的研究报告，揭示老年人AI学习的六大类型：老学霸、老顽童、老明星、老财迷、老当家、老伙伴。超半数学习者动机与能力提升、价值变现深度绑定...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-ai-creation-golden-rules.html\">📝 AI创作黄金10条<br><small class=\"title-en\">AI Creation Golden Rules: 10 Ways to Stand Out</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ AI, 内容创作</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-ai-creation-golden-rules.html\">AI创作时代，如何让你的内容脱颖而出？这10条黄金法则，帮你打造杰出内容！从明确目标受众、善用但不依赖AI工具、打造个人IP到内容深度挖掘与情感共鸣，全面覆盖AI创作要点...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-gold-price-analysis.html\">💰 金价跌破4500：联储按兵不动与4月回调风险<br><small class=\"title-en\">Gold Below $4,500: Fed on Hold & April Pullback Risk</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 财经, 投资分析</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-gold-price-analysis.html\">金价从5400多美元跌至4491美元，跌幅近17%。美联储暂停降息、美元强势回归，市场预期2026年4月可能重演2015年暴跌剧本...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-weekend-market-shock.html\">📈 油价飙升美股暴跌，国内融资松绑与消费补贴<br><small class=\"title-en\">Oil Spike, US Plunge: Refinance Easing & Subsidies</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 财经, 市场分析</div>\n                        <div class=\