{"type":"message","id":"4b9f3d3d","parentId":"42776dcb","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:38:05.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"部署已经完成。让我给用户一个完整的进展汇报。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ 任务完成！**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 进展汇报\n\n| 步骤 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1. 抓取文章 | ✅ | 使用 Playwright 成功获取微信文章内容 |\n| 2. 创建文章 | ✅ | `posts/2026-04-02-women-ai-cofounders.html` |\n| 3. 词汇标注 | ✅ | 29个重点词汇（venture capital, gender gap, entrepreneur等） |\n| 4. 规范检查 | ✅ | 无相邻 word-block 违规 |\n| 5. 更新首页 | ✅ | index.html 已添加新文章链接 |\n| 6. Git 提交 | ✅ | 已 push 到 Gitee |\n| 7. EdgeOne 部署 | ✅ | 部署成功 |\n\n---\n\n## 📄 文章信息\n\n**标题:** 💡 她，中国最牛合伙人  \n**英文:** The Power Partners Behind China's AI Giants  \n**日期:** 2026-04-02  \n**标签:** 科技, 创投, 人物\n\n**内容概要:** 介绍摩尔线程周苑、MiniMax贠烨祎、沐曦彭莉——三家千亿市值硬科技企业背后的女性联合创始人。从英伟达、AMD到独角兽CTO，她们正在打破性别偏见，重新定义科技创业版图。\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 访问链接\n\n- **EdgeOne:** https://mingox-dzlbtybw.edgeone.cool\n- **Gitee Pages:** https://siglea.gitee.io/news\n\n---\n\n如需继续处理其他文章，发送 `MX <链接>` 即可。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":31494,"output":358,"cacheRead":28928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775097467924}}
